-- Harry Winston Diamond names new CFO
-- 
-- Sun Jan 20, 2008 5:32pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/20/businesspro-harrywinstondiamond-cfo-dc-idUSWEN347820080120

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Harry Winston Diamond Corp HW.TO 
said on Sunday Alan Mayne would join as the company's chief 
financial officer, effective immediately. 

  Mayne is replacing Alice Murphy who is leaving company, it 
said. Mayne most recently was chief financial officer of 
Canadian media company, CHUM Limited.  (Reporting by  Paritosh Bansal ; editing by Carol Bishopric)